import React from 'react'
import {Switch, Route} from 'react-router'

import clothes from 'containers/clothes'
import clothe from 'containers/clothe'
import Basket from 'containers/basket'

export default (
  <Switch>
    <Route path='/' component={clothes} exact />
    <Route path='/basket' component={Basket} />
    <Route path='/categories/:id' component={clothes} />
    <Route path='/size/:id' component={clothes} />
    <Route path='/clothes/:id' component={clothe} />
  </Switch>
)
